name: 4 Ring Gyro Fidget
description: A fast-spinning gyro fidget with 4 rings that provides endless fidgeting fun. Print-in-place design takes less than 25 minutes to print using less than 8 grams of filament.

name: OTF Fidget Knife
description: Out-The-Front fidget knife with smooth OTF action made from just 3 printed parts. Perfect for restless hands with realistic knife mechanics.

name: Twelve-in-One Fidget Toy Set
description: An exquisite twelve-in-one fidget toy featuring multiple stress-relief mechanisms including buttons, dials, ratchets, levers, joysticks and clickers in one compact design.

name: Fidget Switch
description: A print-in-place button/switch with a loud satisfying click. Fast to print with very pleasant tactile feedback perfect for fidgeting.

name: Infinity Cube Fidget Toy
description: A satisfying infinity cube that flips and transforms endlessly. Made from interconnected cubes that provide smooth tactile feedback.

name: Stress Ball Fidget
description: Squeezable stress ball with textured surface for tactile stimulation. Perfect size for pocket carry and desk use.

name: Fidget Slider
description: Smooth sliding mechanism with satisfying click endpoints. Compact design perfect for one-handed operation.

name: Gear Fidget Spinner
description: Multi-gear fidget spinner with interlocking gears that create mesmerizing motion patterns.

name: DNA Helix Keychain
description: Beautiful double helix DNA structure keychain with rotating segments. Educational and stylish accessory.

name: Maze Cube Keychain
description: 3D printed maze cube keychain with internal ball bearing. Challenge yourself to navigate the maze.

name: Geometric Crystal Keychain
description: Elegant geometric crystal design with faceted surfaces that catch light beautifully.

name: Mini Tool Keychain
description: Functional mini tool keychain with screwdriver tips and hex keys. Practical everyday carry item.

name: Articulated Dragon Keychain
description: Fully articulated dragon keychain with moveable joints and detailed scales.

name: Flexi Elephant Keychain
description: Adorable flexible elephant keychain with segmented body that bends and poses.

name: Modular Hex Keychain
description: Modular hexagonal keychain system that connects multiple pieces together.

name: Pokemon Trading Card Holder
description: Protective card holder designed specifically for Pokemon trading cards with snap-fit closure.

name: MTG Deck Box
description: Secure deck box for Magic: The Gathering cards with magnetic closure and dice storage.

name: Card Dividers Set
description: Complete set of customizable card dividers for organizing trading card collections.

name: Dice Tower Gaming Set
description: Collapsible dice tower with rolling tray for tabletop gaming sessions.

name: Card Sleeve Dispenser
description: Automatic card sleeve dispenser for easy access during card organizing sessions.
